 BamBam 辞去“Bam's House”主持人职务，KISS OF LIFE 的 Natty 接任https://www.nme.com/news/music/bambam-steps-down-as-host-of-bams-house-kiss-of-lifes-natty-to-take-over-3810388?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=bambam-steps-down-as-host-of-bams-house-kiss-of-lifes-natty-to-takeoverGladys Yeo Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:31:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3810388 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="bambam got7 生命之吻 natty Bam 的房子" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “虽然很难过，但我想更专注于我的主业——音乐”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bambam-steps-down-as-host-of-bams-house-kiss-of-lifes-natty-to-take-over-3810388">BamBam 辞去“Bam&#39;s House”主持人职务，由 KISS OF LIFE 的 Natty 接任的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="bambam got7 生命之吻 natty Bam 的房子" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bambam-natty-bams-house-071124-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/got7">GOT7</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bambam">BamBam</a>辞去了 YouTube 脱口秀节目<em>Bam&#39;s House</em>主持人的职务，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kiss-of-life">KISS OF LIFE</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/natty">Natty</a>接任。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/pow-kpop-interview-boyfriend-girlfriend-avril-lavigne-remake-3807782">战俘接受他们的失败者地位：“我们没有最具爆炸性的开局，但人们正在为我们加油”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（11月6日）， <em>Bam&#39;s House</em> YouTube频道上传了BamBam的视频公告。在视频中，这位 GOT7 歌手表示他将辞去 YouTube 节目主持人的职务。</p><p> “我给你留下这段视频信息是因为我有很多消息要分享，”他说。 “虽然很伤心，但我想更多地专注于我的主要职业——音乐。我决定退出<em>巴姆之家</em>。”</p><p>这位GOT7歌手接着感谢频道观众的喜爱和支持，以及出现在节目中的嘉宾。 “分享这个消息已经让我心痛，让我充满悲伤，”BamBam 说。</p><p>随后他表示，该节目将继续进行，KISS OF LIFE 歌手纳蒂将担任新主持人。 “她作为另一个‘韩国泰国人’非常成功，而且工作非常努力，”他补充道。 “希望大家继续支持Natty的新开始和<em>Bam&#39;s House</em>的新开始。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[SUB]굿바 Been 나의 뱀집(ENG/TH)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/80PQFzbi6_4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>结束前，这位歌手还向曾是他和GOT7前经纪公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/jyp-entertainment">JYP Entertainment</a>旗下练习生的KISS OF LIFE歌手致以最美好的祝愿。</p><p> “我没见过你当练习生，但我一直看到你表现得很好。看到你的成功让我很高兴。”他说。 “现在，不再是<em>巴姆家</em>，而是<em>蒂蒂家了</em>。”</p><p>这位 GOT7 歌手大约两年前首次创办了<em>Bam&#39;s House</em> ，邀请过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a>的 Sakura、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girls-generation">少女时代</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taeyeon">泰妍</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/twice">TWICE</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nayeon">Nayeon</a>等嘉宾。</p><p> BamBam最近发行的是今年8月的第三张个人迷你专辑《Bamesis》。这位歌手还于 2023 年末举办了他的首次“Area 52”世界巡演，随后于今年 5 月在曼谷举办了一场安可演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bambam-steps-down-as-host-of-bams-house-kiss-of-lifes-natty-to-take-over-3810388">BamBam 辞去“Bam&#39;s House”主持人职务，由 KISS OF LIFE 的 Natty 接任的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
罗伯特·帕丁森的《米奇17岁》再次推迟https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattinsons-mickey-17-has-been-delayed-again-3810389?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=robert-pattinsons-mickey-17-has-been-再次延迟Surej SinghThu, 07 Nov 2024 05:25:52 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3810389 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>然而，它的延迟意味着它现在将在 IMAX 中放映</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattinsons-mickey-17-has-been-delayed-again-3810389">罗伯特·帕丁森 (Robert Pattinson) 的《米奇 17》再次推迟的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/robert-pattinson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-pattinson">罗伯特·帕丁森</a>主演的<em>《米奇 17》</em>的上映日期被推迟了几个月 - 请在下面了解有关该电影新上映窗口的更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/parasite-review-bong-joon-ho-2602190#:~:text=His%20latest%20film%2C%20a%20darkly,nothing%20short%20of%20a%20masterpiece.">《寄生虫》评论：奉俊昊的黑色喜剧惊悚片是一部现代杰作（是的，即使有字幕）</a></strong></li></ul><p>据 Variety 报道，即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bong-joon-ho">奉俊昊</a>执导的科幻黑色喜剧电影将推迟三个月，从 1 月 31 日上映推迟到 2025 年 4 月 18 日。</p><p>根据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/mickey-17-release-date-april-robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-1236203196/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Variety》</em></a>发言人的一份声明，这部由华纳兄弟发行的电影现在将在 4 月份在 IMAX 上放映：“当 4 月 18 日上映日期确定时，我们迅速采取行动以确保上映日期为<em>米奇 17</em> 。我们对新的上映日期感到非常兴奋，也很高兴这部电影将在 IMAX 上向观众上映。” </p><figure id="attachment_3794652" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794652" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794652" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/robert-pattinson-bong-joon-ho-mickey-17@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794652" class="wp-caption-text">奉俊昊和罗伯特·帕丁森。图片来源：RONDA CHURCHILL/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>档期的改变源于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jackson-biopic-delayed-to-late-2025-3809939">本周早些时候宣布的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>传记片《<em>迈克尔》</em>的档期从 4 月 18 日推迟到 10 月 3 日。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattison-cant-stop-dying-in-mickey-17-trailer-3794650"><em>《米奇 17》</em>的第一部完整预告片于 9 月发布</a>，展示了罗伯特·帕丁森饰演的米奇的各种克隆体在探索冰星球的探险中死去的情景。这部电影的主演还有娜奥米·阿基、史蒂文·元、托妮·科莱特、马克·鲁法洛、荷丽黛·格兰杰等。</p><p> <em>《米奇 17》</em>将是俊浩继 2019 年广受好评的<i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/parasite-review-bong-joon-ho-2602190">《寄生虫》</a>之后的首部电影作品，</i>该片于次年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2020-winners-list-2606712">荣获</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡金像奖</a>最佳影片奖。 <em>《寄生虫》</em>也成为韩国历史上票房最高的电影。</p><p>这部电影改编自 2022 年的小说<em>《米奇7</em> 》，于 2022 年首次宣布上映，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mickey-17-teaser-trailer-bong-joon-ho-robert-pattinson-release-date-3361290">于同年发布了预告片</a>。这部电影原定于今年上映，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/bong-joon-ho-fans-furious-at-film-delay-3568663">由于去年演员和编剧的罢工而被无限期推迟，</a>现在推迟到 2025 年 1 月上映。 </p><figure id="attachment_3384792" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3384792" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3384792" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new.jpg" alt="罗伯特·帕丁森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Robert-Pattinson-batman-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3384792" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·帕丁森。图片来源：Cindy Ord/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《米奇 17》</em>将于 2025 年 4 月 18 日在电影院首映。</p><p>瑞安·达利 (Rhian Daly) 在《寄生虫<em>》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/parasite-review-bong-joon-ho-2602190#:~:text=His%20latest%20film%2C%20a%20darkly,nothing%20short%20of%20a%20masterpiece."><em>的</em>五星级评论</a>中写道：“ <em>《寄生虫》</em>的部分精彩之处在于，虽然这是一个‘我们与他们’的故事，但它不选边站。相反，奉俊昊将两个家庭的缺陷都展现得淋漓尽致——每个家庭都像另一个家庭一样寄生，金氏家族以虚假借口钻进朴家的房子，而朴氏则巧妙地利用了金氏家族，同时对他们发表了贬低性的评论，这些言论给了他们自己的机会。一种优越感。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattinsons-mickey-17-has-been-delayed-again-3810389">罗伯特·帕丁森 (Robert Pattinson) 的《米奇 17》再次推迟的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
